      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and she\u2019s looking for a new home! This car has been super reliable and is still in really great shape. It's been well-maintained and drives like a dream\u2014perfect for your daily commute or a weekend getaway. You're going to love how it handles! Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
