    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sound example of BMW\u2019s high-revving pinnacle. Powered by the S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies, the engine pulls cleanly to its 8,000 RPM redline. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement to ensure structural rigidity under high lateral loads. The Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox offers precise throws, paired with a factory limited-slip differential that remains tight. The suspension features refreshed bushings and dampers, maintaining the chassis's legendary communicative feedback. While the finish shows minor stone chips and light interior bolster wear indicative of a driven enthusiast vehicle, the drivetrain is dialed in for immediate performance.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 9
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
