    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle strikes the perfect balance between luxury and everyday utility. Finished in a classic exterior that retains its deep luster, the body shows only minor signs of use consistent with careful ownership. Under the hood, the engine runs exceptionally smooth, having benefited from a consistent maintenance schedule and recent fluid services. The transmission shifts seamlessly, and the suspension remains firm yet comfortable, providing a confident driving experience. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of comfort; the upholstery is well-preserved, the dashboard is free of cracks, and every electronic feature\u2014from the dual-zone climate control to the premium sound system\u2014functions exactly as it should. This car has been garage-kept and smoke-free, making it an ideal choice for someone seeking a reliable, high-quality vehicle that has been treated with genuine care.",
      "price": 36850.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
